videos.headline: Clark banks in the floater
videos.description: Caitlin Clark gets into the lane and flips in the floater off the glass.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Clark banks in the floater) 2023/03/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Caitlin Clark comes off the screen and splashes a 3
videos.description: Caitlin Clark is able to knock down the wing 3-pointer, extending the Hawkeyes lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Caitlin Clark comes off the screen and splashes a 3) 2023/03/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Caitlin Clark steals inbounds pass for and-1
videos.description: Caitlin Clark picks off the inbounds pass and gets the and-1 to start the second quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Caitlin Clark steals inbounds pass for and-1) 2023/03/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Caitlin Clark swings pass to Hannah Stuelke for the layup
videos.description: Caitlin Clark rips a pass down low to Hannah Stuelke for the easy layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Caitlin Clark swings pass to Hannah Stuelke for the layup) 2023/03/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Caitlin Clark splashes 3 from long range
videos.description: Caitlin Clark steps back and drains the 3-pointer from well beyond the arc.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Caitlin Clark splashes 3 from long range) 2023/03/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Monika Czinano beats 3rd-quarter buzzer for Iowa
videos.description: Caitlin Clark finds a rolling Monika Czinano for the layup right before the 3rd-quarter buzzer sounds.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Monika Czinano beats 3rd-quarter buzzer for Iowa) 2023/03/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Caitlin Clark drops 26 points and dishes 12 assists in first-round win
videos.description: Caitlin Clark gets her 2023 tournament off to a great start as she scores 26 points and gives out 12 assists in Iowa's dominant first-round win.
